2	 * Plan Editor Screen (Push page)
3	 *
4	 * Create or edit a training plan. Provides:
5	 * - Plan name input
6	 * - Plan mode selector (无限循环/固定周期)
7	 * - Schedule mode selector (每周固定日/固定间隔)
8	 * - Weekly fixed: weekday toggle buttons, assign training type per weekday
9	 * - Fixed interval: rest days stepper, training day order list
10	 * - Save validation
11	 */
